      <title>以色列官员在债券发售前在伦敦会见投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/israel-officials-meet-investors-in-london-before-eurobond-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，一群以色列政府官员本周将在伦敦与投资者会面，该国计划在第一季度发行欧元债券。由于会议是私下举行的，这些知情人士不愿透露姓名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/israel-officials-meet-investors-in-london-before-eurobond-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 09:55:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国零售商股价因对经济的担忧加剧而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/retailers-fall-hit-by-rising-investor-concerns-about-uk-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们对英国经济的担忧加剧以及工党增税预算的影响超过了假日季强劲的销售业绩，英国零售商股票遭遇抛售，特易购 (Tesco Plc) 和玛莎百货 (Marks &amp; Spencer Group Plc) 受到重创。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/retailers-fall-hit-by-rising-investor-concerns-about-uk-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 08:53:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国市场抛售加剧，英镑跌至年内最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/pound-slumps-to-weakest-since-2023-amid-broad-uk-market-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心借贷成本飙升导致工党政府难以控制赤字，英镑跌至一年多来的最低点，股市下跌，英国政府债券连续第四天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/pound-slumps-to-weakest-since-2023-amid-broad-uk-market-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 07:04:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国债结束四天抛售；英国资产暴跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受全球债券需求强劲信号的影响，美国国债本周首日上涨，结束了因投资者对政府债务和通胀上升的担忧而引发的抛售。英国资产继续遭受重创。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 22:28:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利拒绝监管机构批准的 30 亿美元铁矿石项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/chile-dismisses-3-billion-iron-project-cleared-by-regulators-m5ogcj3j</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利官员否决了一项采矿和港口项目，这是十多年来就一项 30 亿美元投资进行的法律和监管审议中出现的最新转折，该项目将环境保护与经济增长对立起来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/chile-dismisses-3-billion-iron-project-cleared-by-regulators-m5ogcj3j</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 22:09:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Seven & i 首席财务官称收购方案仍缺乏足够细节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/seven-i-convenience-store-recovery-hits-wider-retail-headwinds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Seven &amp; i Holdings Co. 首席财务官 Yoshimichi Maruyama 表示，该公司董事会的一个特别委员会仍在考虑 Alimentation Couche-Tard Inc. 及其创始人伊藤家族的收购提议，尽管目前还没有足够的信息来评估这些提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/seven-i-convenience-store-recovery-hits-wider-retail-headwinds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Amundi、EDF 与多家公司联手要求欧盟不要削弱 ESG 规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/amundi-edf-among-firms-asking-eu-not-to-water-down-esg-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[包括 Amundi SA 和法国电力公司 (Electricite de France SA) 在内的一些法国最大的公司已签署了一封致欧洲政策制定者的信函，敦促他们确保欧盟坚持当前实施 ESG 报告规则的时间表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/amundi-edf-among-firms-asking-eu-not-to-water-down-esg-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 16:57:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
